OL,6,FProposals for new train services that
OL,7,Fconnects London to north Wales have
OL,8,Fbeen announced.
OL,10,FTrain and rail infrastructure supplier
OL,11,FAlstom said it plans to offer
OL,12,Fpassengers new direct links, quicker
OL,13,Fjourneys and "more competitive fares".
OL,15,FIt has been 13 years since train
OL,16,Fcompany Wrexham & Shropshire ` which
OL,17,Foperated between London Marylebone and
OL,18,Fvia Shrewsbury ` came to a halt due to
OL,19,Flosses.
