OL,6,FThat train company itself had started
OL,7,Fafter a 40-year hiatus for direct
OL,8,Ftrains between Wrexham and London.
OL,10,FThe proposed service - known as
OL,11,F'Wrexham, Shropshire and Midlands
OL,12,FRailway (WSMR), is expected to run
OL,13,Ffrom 2025 between London Euston and
OL,14,FWrexham up to five times per day in
OL,15,Fboth directions.
OL,17,FIt comes as Avanti West Coast will be
OL,18,Fwithdrawing its current daily return
OL,19,Fservice between London Euston and
OL,20,FShrewsbury in June.
