OL,6,FTrains would call at Wrexham, Gobowen,
OL,7,FShrewsbury, Telford Central,
OL,8,FWolverhampton, Walsall, Coleshill
OL,9,FParkway, Nuneaton, Milton Keynes and
OL,10,Fwhen a new station opens, Darlaston.
OL,12,FThe line is expected to dramatically
OL,13,Freduce travel times.
OL,15,FRail minister Hew Merriman said:
OL,16,F"These exciting proposals could see
OL,17,Fbetter connections for communities
OL,18,Facross north Wales and the Midlands,
OL,19,Fincluding direct services to London
OL,20,Ffrom Shrewsbury, Telford and Wrexham.
