OL,6,F"Competition delivers choice for
OL,7,Fpassengers and drives up standards,
OL,8,Fwhich is why we continue to work with
OL,9,Findustry to help make the most of open
OL,10,Faccess rail."
OL,12,FMost train operators in England are
OL,13,Fpaid a management fee, with the UK
OL,14,FGovernment holding responsibility for
OL,15,Fcosts and revenue.
OL,17,FHowever, ScotRail and Transport for
OL,18,FWales Rail are under public ownership.
