OL,6,FAlstom is the largest private rail
OL,7,Foperator in North America but if its
OL,8,FWSMR plans get the go ahead it will be
OL,9,Fthe first time it has run services in
OL,10,Fthe UK.
OL,12,FThe company's managing director in the
OL,13,FUK and Ireland, Nick Crossfield, said:
OL,14,F"Alstom is also committed to embedding
OL,15,Fsustainability into every element of
OL,16,Four organisation, and WSMR will help
OL,17,Fdrive a modal shift from road to rail
OL,18,Fby offering a greener alternative for
OL,19,Ftravellers across England and Wales."
